-- =============================================================
--  SCRIPT 03 — PRODUCT & USER BEHAVIOR: COHORT & RETENTION
--  Domain:  Product & User Behavior
--  Type:    Cohort & Retention Analysis
--  Dialect: Standard SQL (portable)
--
--  Analyses covered:
--    • Monthly acquisition cohorts
--    • Retention curve (M0 → M6)
--    • Churn by cohort month
--    • Average sessions & feature adoption by cohort
--    • Time-to-first-value (TTFV)
-- =============================================================


WITH

